		<div class="inner clearfix">
			<div class="col-md-11 col-sm-11 col-xs-12 no-padding">
				<h1>What Do You Get When You Fall In Love?</h1>
<div class="excerpt">Let&#39;s consider the words of the song &quot;I&#39;ll Never Fall In Love&quot; by Burt Bacharach and Hal David: &quot;What do you get when you kiss a girl? You get enough germs to catch pneumonia After you do, she&#39;ll never phone ya I&#39;ll never fall in love again&quot; OK, it&#39;s confession time. I am single and</div>
<div class="post-meta">
    <div class="wls-authors">
            </div>
    <span class="meta">
		<span class="strong">
			<time datetime="2010-03-08 04:28:25">8 Mar 2010 - 04:28AM</time>
		</span>
			</span>
</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>	

            <div class="content">
                <div class="social-wrapper" id="social-sharer">
